IMPORTANT: The C Object System requires GNU make 3.81 or higher.

Compilation and run:
--------------------

from each subdirectories:

make release.run

or (assuming COS is installed or LD_LIBRARY_PATH set appropriately):

make release
./arch/bin/cos-ex01

Debugging makefiles:
--------------------

make [target] SHOW=yes TRACE=yes

# debug flags
SHOW  will show the commands run
TRACE will show the value of important variables

Project information:
--------------------
  - web page: http:/cern.ch/laurent.deniau/cos.html
